  • Deprecated Classes
    Class
    Description
    io.atlasmap.actions.ExpressionFieldAction
    expression is now decleared at Mapping level and processed directly in DefaultAtlasContext.
    io.atlasmap.core.DefaultAtlasCombineStrategy
    AtlasCombineStrategy.
    io.atlasmap.core.DefaultAtlasSeparateStrategy
    AtlasSeparateStrategy.
    io.atlasmap.java.v2.JavaCollection
    Collection.
    io.atlasmap.v2.ActionListUpgradeDeserializer
    This was introduced for backward compatibility. Remove this in v2.0. https://github.com/atlasmap/atlasmap/pull/877
    io.atlasmap.v2.ADMDigest
    Document metadata, specification and mapping definition are stored separately. This is kept only for backward compatibility.
    io.atlasmap.v2.Collection
    collection field is now handled vertically and this is not in use. However, we might want to resurrect it to support one-to-many/many-to-one for each collection, see https://github.com/atlasmap/atlasmap/issues/1236
    io.atlasmap.v2.DataSourceMetadata
    io.atlasmap.v2.Expression
    Expression field action is deprecated. Mapping level expression has to be used instead.
    io.atlasmap.v2.ValueContainer
